{"tid":1473470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[清算派]1823 各區投訴個案長期討論區 1","createTime":"2019-08-15T00:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:28:29.000Z","uid":57328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5805a13feb8040239e6387bc67704ccc95dddc","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"為左令清算藍絲廢老黑社會成為社會習慣，我決定開一個長期討論區，方便伸張正義既巴絲能熟習投訴技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2969d930f95045077babab3dc07516e87bd04eec","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"iOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?mt=8&amp;l=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftell-me-1823%2Fid426069047%3Fmt%3D8%26l%3Dzh&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=718d4d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?mt=8&amp;l=zh</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823&amp;hl=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823%26hl%3Dzh&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=4467411a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823&amp;hl=zh</a><br />\n<br />\n大家係未見到廢老都眼火爆，咁請你地每個人將怒火化為力量，將投訴廢老變成每日習慣，搞到佢地雞犬不寧。 好多巴打已經做緊，你都一齊加入啦！<br />\n<br />\n用法：<br />\n1. 下載APP<br />\n2. 投訴<br />\n3. 揀地點, 講發生咩事<br />\n4. 有專人幫你跟進, 一定要回覆你<br />\n<br />\n違泊 (特別係紀律部隊宿舍附近)<br />\n阻塞行人過路處<br />\n冷氣機滴水<br />\n食店唔乾淨<br />\n塞渠<br />\n路標唔清晰<br />\n佔用官地<br />\n僭建<br />\n地面不平<br />\n維修公園設施<br />\n鋪頭霸佔行人路<br />\n個鐵欄/條柱變形<br />\n有蚊<br />\n有雜草<br />\n有老鼠<br />\n無入咪錶<br />\n燈光唔夠<br />\n<br />\n每一次都要細範圍咁講<br />\n例如冷氣滴水唔好用街名，用大廈，一座座大廈玩，開file都開死佢，長玩長有。只要有創意，乜都有得投訴，齊來改善社區環境！<br />\n<br />\n記住cc埋俾CE Office (ceo@ceo.gov.hk)<br />\n寫住要書面回覆 同 e.g. 行動日期, 檢控數字 等<br />\n<br />\n總知你睇唔過眼, 覺得佢犯法就投訴得"},{"pid":"97136b8728aae5134112c86e51a05d39e8802177","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2947538895288225?s=1355234439&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197517173623758%2Fposts%2F2947538895288225%3Fs%3D1355234439%26sfns%3Dmo&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a25b1f1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2947538895288225?s=1355234439&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n雲海 陳雲海<br />\n剛剛<br />\n機場管理局擔心示威者再次佔據，你用法律去申請法庭禁制令！Ok！但你都唔可以犯法做啲咁無賴嘅嘢！今朝有機場人員向我透露，機管局唔單止用水馬，仲用索帶加固綁起大部分機場T1 T2走火通道。呢個係完全違反消防條例嘅做法！機場人員同我講，大家如果發現機場任何走火通道比AA落鐵馬欄左，請打27238787消防投訴熱線投訴，24小時，唔一定要留名！我哋一齊鼓勵機管局守法好冇？！（相片屬於今朝早機場8:00時間情況）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zGc53Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zGc53Z.jpg&h=ae8e1eed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f130ae749915825f01dbcfdcaebc4d27a11511bf","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1105415176319776?s=1355234439&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107233492804621%2Fposts%2F1105415176319776%3Fs%3D1355234439%26sfns%3Dmo&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=3f3626fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1105415176319776?s=1355234439&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【謎底終於解開】荃灣區內湧現違例橫額，究竟邊個掛出來？<br />\n<br />\n這幾日，荃灣區內湧現違例橫額，意圖抹黑反送中示威者。這麼有組織的行動，究竟背後是甚麼人做的？這個謎底終於解開！<br />\n<br />\n晚上11時許，荃威花園出現白色 Honda 私家車（車牌RS1192）接載三名男子正在懸掛同款違例橫額。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署註冊資料，該輛私家車登記車主「池月明先生」報稱居於屯門翠寧花園第1座某單位。有網民指出，池月明在廈門有經營生意，可能與近期活躍於荃灣「福建幫」有關係。<br />\n<br />\n#街坊來圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJN7UYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJN7UYn.jpg&h=731aa3a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18905387e799899497ea085df1bae3bae8d0480c","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:47:00.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位清算派匯報各區1823事項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4b5fde494d8cd6352ff65edebf78a75a9755e2","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"交通銀行突然要求分行掛國旗效忠，平時只有十一先會掛。（圖為軒尼詩道及牛頭角分行）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3dfjvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3dfjvg.jpg&h=13d61383&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saiSmJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaiSmJC.jpg&h=8cc50f76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpcPoWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpcPoWY.jpg&h=41b22129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環分行 上環都有"},{"pid":"02d5b36e46dad86ccbfad41bfe49b0d106800b4e","tid":1473470,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985e85740bc6d1d9244a48b79afd732de6dc430b","tid":1473470,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"我投訴阻街好耐,食環一路都唔撚理我,之後去申訴專員投訴到條友要寫報告<br />\n後來我再次投訴阻街,食環搵左第二個人負責,佢叫間舖將阻街既野搬去馬路度<br />\n之後同我講,食環負責行人路,佢依家阻馬路,你搵警察啦<br />\n去到呢一步,我已經冇晒計了"},{"pid":"4ec8041c3ebbb22164e5ed1d942a6d3ddac4c817","tid":1473470,"uid":186494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"985e85740bc6d1d9244a48b79afd732de6dc430b","tid":1473470,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"我投訴阻街好耐,食環一路都唔撚理我,之後去申訴專員投訴到條友要寫報告<br />\n後來我再次投訴阻街,食環搵左第二個人負責,佢叫間舖將阻街既野搬去馬路度<br />\n之後同我講,食環負責行人路,佢依家阻馬路,你搵警察啦<br />\n去到呢一步,我已經冇晒計了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"拍片，之後send去1823，投訴食環批準佔領馬路。"},{"pid":"ef267e8f14ef18af04e6b69edb1e0ef4d56c96f9","tid":1473470,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec8041c3ebbb22164e5ed1d942a6d3ddac4c817","tid":1473470,"uid":186494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"985e85740bc6d1d9244a48b79afd732de6dc430b","tid":1473470,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"我投訴阻街好耐,食環一路都唔撚理我,之後去申訴專員投訴到條友要寫報告<br />\n後來我再次投訴阻街,食環搵左第二個人負責,佢叫間舖將阻街既野搬去馬路度<br />\n之後同我講,食環負責行人路,佢依家阻馬路,你搵警察啦<br />\n去到呢一步,我已經冇晒計了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"拍片，之後send去1823，投訴食環批準佔領馬路。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"投訴過啦,個食環話佢負責行人路<br />\n佢叫個舖頭清左D阻街野佢,但個舖頭搬去行人路以外既地方佢就冇權管<br />\n你搵警察啦(時值7月,佢都知班狗唔會理你)"},{"pid":"afd850d97174b9c31c8299b3a7993bf469bd8146","tid":1473470,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f130ae749915825f01dbcfdcaebc4d27a11511bf","tid":1473470,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1105415176319776?s=1355234439&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107233492804621%2Fposts%2F1105415176319776%3Fs%3D1355234439%26sfns%3Dmo&d=uCt0J